<HEADLINE>
<P>
MORNING REPORT: POP/ROCK 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By BETH KLEID , Arts and entertainment reports from The Times, national and 
international news services and the nation's press. 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
In Black's Shoes: Clint Black, the 1989 Country Music Assn.'s Horizon Award 
winner, will debut his upcoming single, "Put Yourself in My Shoes," on the 24th 
annual "CMA Awards Show" Oct. 8. The single, scheduled to be released to radio 
