<HEADLINE>
<P>
ORANGE COUNTY FOCUS: NEWPORT BEACH; 
</P>
<P>
CITY TO HOLD TOUR OF BIKE TRAIL NETWORK 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
In an effort to reacquaint residents with the Newport Beach bicycle trail 
network, the city is holding its sixth annual Great Newport Beach Bicycle Tour 
on Oct. 7 at 10 a.m. 
</P>
<P>
Participants will tour the approximately 9 miles of trails along the Upper Back 
Bay bikeway and Back Bay Drive and also have an opportunity to view 
demonstrations on bicycle maintenance and safety. 
</P>
<P>
For additional information and registration, phone the city's Public Works 
Department at (714) 644-3311. 
</P>
