<HEADLINE>
<P>
NIBBLES AND BITS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Members of the New York City Ballet will be guests Sept. 30 at a "Stars and 
Stripes" dinner-dance and fund-raiser for the Center Dance Alliance, an Orange 
County Performing Arts Center support group. The gala will follow the troupe's 
final matinee performance at the Center. Information: (714) 556-2122, Ext. 220 
or 222. 
</P>
