SUN MICROSYSTEMS GETS GE AEROSPACE CONTRACT 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By United Press International 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
MOUNTAIN VIEW, Calif. 
</P>
