EMPLOYEES; WORKING HOURS; DEPARTMENT OF THE TREASURY (U.S.); ECONOMIC 
SANCTIONS; UNITED STATES -- FOREIGN INVESTMENTS -- IRAQ; ASSETS 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
