<P>
Chart, DOW JONES INDUSTRIALS ; Chart, FOREIGN EXCHANGE ; Chart, DOW JONES 
AVERAGES ; Chart, MARKET INDEX ; Chart, VOLUME LEADERS ; Chart, METALS 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
